d be comfortable building the "brain" of the application (RAG, Agentic orch=
estration) as well as the "body" (FastAPI backends, Next.js frontends, and =
Dockerized infrastructure).</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>=
<ul><li><p><strong>Agentic Orchestration &amp; Skills:</strong> Develop and=
