mbeddings and data retrieval strategies to securely connect LLMs with enter=
prise data for high-accuracy outputs.</p></li><li><p><strong>Full-Stack App=
lication Development:</strong> Design and implement both frontend and backe=
nd components using <strong>Next.js</strong> and <strong>FastAPI</strong>. =
